  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Biphasic Remogliflozin Etabonate in the Treatment of Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <acronym>BRID</acronym>
  <official_title>A 12-week Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel-group, Placebo-controlled Study to Determine the Efficacy and Safety of Biphasic Remogliflozin Etabonate When Administered to Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
