  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a dose-ranging study to evaluate the efficacy, safety and tolerability of a range of
      doses of a biphasic formulation of remogliflozin etabonate compared to placebo, administered
      over 12 weeks in subjects with type 2 diabetes mellitus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
